name: primordial soup of OBJKTs
description: @WorldArtDay2021 #WorldArtDay2021 #NFTsForAll || Primordial soup - a set of early conditions, buzzing plasma of reactive elements that eventually lead to something greater, gradually forming structure, rhythm, life. The early days of hic et nunc and sudden growth of art NFT popularity is noisy and full of opinions, uncertainty, excitement and potential. The hope is to decentralize, open up and diversify art market and consumption as we know it. This is the vision of life to come from this soup.
